UNDATED: the witch. 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Developing a Network of Informants
</P>
<P>
   Let the process begin with a general citation affixed to the
walls of the parish church or the town hall ((which notice would)
direct, command, require and admonish [reporting to the
Inquisition)) if anyone know, see, or have heard that any person is
reported to be a heretic or a witch.
</P>
<P>
   Spiritual Value of Bad Hair Days
</P>
<P>
   ((Demons)) seem chiefly to molest women and girls with beautiful
hair, either because they devote themselves too much to the care
and adornment of their hair, or because they are wont to excite men
by means of their hair, or because they are boastfully vain about
it . . . Far more women are witches then men . . . yet men are more
often bewitched than women.
