   w/CUBA-TOURISM _ VARADERO, Cuba _ With a passion for large-mouth
bass, Austin-resident Dan Snow is always searching for the one that
got away. And he's always searching in Cuba, a communist country
just 90 miles south of Florida, but off limits to most U.S.
citizens. ``They will have to lock me up and throw away the key to
keep me from going to Cuba because I just love that place,''
exclaimed the former Marine, whose business is simply called Bass
Tours. Snow's not the only one. (Emling, Cox News Service)
