<HEADLINE>
NEW AMERICA NEWS SERVICE BUDGET _ RECTIFICATION
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS:
<TEXT>
<P>
   The headline on Bill Maxwell's column in this week's New America
News Service _ `Bloody Sunday' With the Reverend _ does not reflect
the events Maxwell describes.
</P>
<P>
   The headline should read:
</P>
<P>
   MARCHING WITH THE REVEREND
</P>
<P>
   Please take note of the rectification. We apologize for this
inconsistency.
</P>
<P>
   Sally-Ann Welford, Editor, New America News Service.
</P>
