<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  Saturday, January 23, 1999
<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL; 
Editors: &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
POPE-CROWDS (Mexico City) _ A story will move at 9 p.m., CDT,
Saturday. By DUDLEY ALTHAUS. Questions, call Jake Doherty at
713-220-7674. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Houston Chronicle  &QL; 
 &QL;
