<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    POPE ELEVATES MEXICO'S ROLE IN CATHOLIC CHURCH, URGES DIGNITY
FOR POOR
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (l) Lifestyle
categories.
 &HT;    By SUSAN FERRISS 
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service 
