<HEADLINE>
SOONERS WOMEN CAN'T STOP LONGHORNS IN SECOND HALF
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MIKE JONES 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
