who vanished from the street near her home in Mesa on Jan. 2, and
hasn't been seen since. ``I have some things to tell you about your
missing daughter's case,'' the clairvoyant told Linda. `'I've been
getting some very strong feelings about it.'' ``Really?'' Linda
said, her voice rising. ``Are you getting the feeling that you're
talking to the wrong Biggs family?'' By E.J. MONTINI Story will
move in the ``A'' and ``K'' categories.
